TextEng: That's why I'm here: I've seeds that need planting.
Text: 그래서 여기 왔어요: 심어야 할 씨앗들이 있어요.

TextEng: I need to go now.
Me have seeds to plant, yuh?
Yuh, me go now.
How about if I give you some extra gold then?
Text: 그럼 추가로 금화를 좀 드리면 어때요?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> What if the druids helped tend your farm?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 드루이드들이 농장을 돌보는 걸 도와주면 어때요?

TextEng: This tree is getting planted even if its roots have to feed on your corpse.
Text: 이 나무는 당신 시체를 뿌리의 양분으로 삼아서라도 심어질 거예요.

TextEng: What if me gives you extra gold?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me gets druids to help you care farm?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 드루이드들 데려와서 농장 돌보는 거 도와줄게?

TextEng: Me plant tree, even if over your dead body, yuh?
Text: 나 나무 심을 거야, 너 죽은 시체 위에라도, 응?

TextEng: Fair enough, just thought I'd ask.
Text: 충분히 공정해요, 그냥 물어봐야 할 것 같아서요.

TextEng: Sorry, me just askin'...
Here, 300 gold, then. That's six good years.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> How does 200 gold sound?
Sorry, I don't think I have enough gold right now.
Text: 미안해요, 지금은 금화가 충분하지 않은 것 같아요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Uh, 200 gold good?
Here, 300 gold. That like... um... two years worth?
Text: 여기, 금화 300개. 그거... 음... 2년 농사 가치 되지?

TextEng: Uh, me no have enough gold right now.
Text: 어... 나 지금 금화 충분히 없어.

TextEng: Who are you?
Who you be?
What do you do here?
What you does here?
I was sent here by Archdruid Aawill.
Me gets sent here by Archdruid Aawill.
This isn't your land, though.
What kind of work do you have to do?
Me wonders what you got doing?
Me doesn't thinking this you land.
Text: 나 이거 너 땅 아니라고 생각해.

TextEng: Where does your property end?
Where you property ended at?
I'm sorry. I didn't know.
Me never knowed that, no.
I'm sorry, but there's some worry that the forest is suffering.
Text: 미안해요, 하지만 숲이 고통받고 있다는 걱정이 있어요.

TextEng: Me sorry. Me just hear others worry about forest.
Text: 나 미안해. 나 다른 사람들 숲 걱정한다고 들었어.

TextEng: Listen buddy, I'm planting these seeds to protect the forest.
Text: 들어봐요, 친구, 나는 숲을 보호하기 위해 이 씨앗들을 심는 거예요.

TextEng: Me sent protecting forest. Me needs planting seeds!
Text: 나 숲 보호하라고 보내졌어. 나 씨앗 심어야 돼!
